Class PlayerMachine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ocr.jeanlouis34.escapegame.player.PlayerMachine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Player
    public class PlayerMachine
extends java.lang.Object
implements Player
    This class is the twin class of Player Machine. This class is only linked with the Jeuchallenger Class in the Challenger pattern. This class enables to compare both automatically and handly made combinaisons. That is why it uses the variables of all the classes about COMBINAISON.
